# STEP 5 — Verify Vite Config

Open:

```text
prayas-foundation/vite.config.ts
```

Ensure:

```ts
import { defineConfig } from "vite";
import react from "@vitejs/plugin-react";

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [react()],
});
```

OR

```ts
import { defineConfig } from "vite";
import react from "@vitejs/plugin-react";

export default defineConfig({
  base: "/",
  plugins: [react()],
});
```

DO NOT USE:

```ts
base: "/prayas-foundation/";
```

---

# STEP 6 — Create React Router Rewrite File

Create file:

```text
public/.htaccess
```

Inside:

```apache
RewriteEngine On

RewriteBase /

RewriteRule ^index\.html$ - [L]

RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d

RewriteRule . /index.html [L]
```

Save.

